levels.levelDescription: Here's a daunting prelude: velvety dark-grass unfurls like a raven-coated carpet, guiding the daring closer to the heart of Eclipsed Dominion. A spectral breeze carries the whispers of fallen souls, giving breath to twisting shades foreboding terror. Rubble from torn innocence juxtaposes with pits, deep-dark-holes yawning with hunger — a token of the land’s cruel jest upon trespassers who infringe its melancholic terrain. Whispers echo the tales of deception and unseen entities willing to drag tenuous threads of bravery into obscurity.

Among captivating dread-covered expanses, walks the smooth weight of tundra-sand feeding into minds the refusal to rekindle light.
